description: This file defines a Note class representing a user-created note entity, including properties such as id, title, content, createdAt, and updatedAt. It also provides methods for copying with modifications, serializing to a map for storage, and deserializing from a map.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: A class representing a note with fields for id, title, content, createdAt, and updatedAt, along with methods to copy, serialize, and deserialize.

methods.name: copyWith
methods.description: Returns a copy of the current Note instance with provided fields updated.

methods.name: toMap
methods.description: Serializes the Note instance to a Map<String, dynamic> suitable for storage.

methods.name: fromMap
methods.description: Creates a Note instance from a Map<String, dynamic> typically retrieved from storage.
